Package structures

Interface BinaryTreeNode<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - they type of data stored in this BinaryTreeNode
    public interface BinaryTreeNode<T>
    A BinaryTreeNode represents a node in a binary tree. It is guaranteed to store some data (cannot hold null) and may have a left child and a right child.
    Author:
    jddevaug
